p: We next investigated the time origin of the best-supported Swiss dominated clusters. For these estimates, monophyletic trees containing 5 or more members and fulfilling a Swiss dominance criterion of 80% ( Table 2) defined a best-supported Swiss cluster. Phylodynamic reinference of these clusters estimated that their origins ranged between (median) October 1999 and June 2007 ( Table 2 and Supplementary Figure 2).
